name: Penelope Cruz
description:
Penélope Cruz is a Spanish actress, winner of an Academy Award for Best Actress in a Supporting Role in 2008.

Even though SD recognizes Penélope quite well without the need for a specific embedding, I've always thought the resemblance was quite improvable (as is the case with many celebrities), and that's what moved me to create this TI, which I hope you'll find an upgrade compared to the "default" SD version.

It's a 1000-step TI trained on a dataset of 18 images with my usual settings.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

How to create a good prompt using my TIs

You're obviously free to experiment, but bear in mind that my TIs are trained with a more or less fixed phrasing, that normally starts with:

"photo of EMBEDDING_NAME, a woman"

So I recommend always starting your prompt like that and then building the rest of the prompt from there. For instance, "photo of (p3cruz:0.99), a woman, RAW, close portrait photo, sexy pirate outfit, pale skin, slim body, (high detailed skin:1.2), 8k uhd, dslr, soft lighting, high quality, film grain, Fujifilm XT3 sharp focus, f 5.6, bandana, holding a gun".
